[[File:Ultima-Pearl.jpg|thumb|right|An Ultima Pearl.]]
'''Ultima Pearls''' were uncommon, silvery, lustrous, spherical [[Pearl/Legends|pearls]] found on the deep ocean floor of [[Dac/Legends|Dac]], that could be used as a form of [[Lightsaber crystal/Legends|lightsaber crystal]]. It required considerable skill to properly install an Ultima Pearl. [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Jedi Master/Legends|Master]] [[Cilghal]] used an ultima-pearl in her [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]].

